<p><em>Hunting season 08</em>, Belconnen Theatre, September 17-21.</p>

<p>Reviewed by Helen Musa</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Devisers of â€œThe Hunting Seasonâ€, a multi-faceted multi-media youth arts project, have threatened to â€œtrack down and murder the arts scenes of this cityâ€. And sure enough, â€œCognition: Part 1,â€ the first work in the projectâ€™s continuing theatre season, throws out a challenge to those of us living in the Brave New World.</p>
